      </p>

     </div>
     <div id="fn" class="footnote"><a class="note-ref" href="#PJA02d120n1-ptr" id="PJA02d120n1">1</a>
      
   <p>Mercys husband, James, had written critically about the Second Provincial Congress to <abbr title="fade=[ on ] fadespeed=[0.1] windowlock=[on] cssbody=[ boxover ] header=[]  body=[ John Adams (17351826) ]">JA</abbr> earlier (<a href="default.xqy?keys=ADMS-print-06-02-02-0077" class="document">20 Feb. 1775</a>, above).</p>

